# wiki/_raw/

In-vault drafts staging. Type fast notes here, then promote to proper wiki pages later by running `ingest raw drafts`.

This is DIFFERENT from `.raw/` at the vault root:

- `.raw/` (root, hidden) — immutable source documents (PDFs, articles, transcripts).
- `wiki/_raw/` (visible in Obsidian) — your own quick drafts that need processing.

The ingest workflow promotes drafts here into proper categorized wiki pages, then DELETES the original draft.
